query {
  ~version: 
}

docs {
  ## Get Price List by ID
  ดึงข้อมูลรายการราคารายการเดียวตาม ID

  Retrieves the full details of a vendor price list including all product prices, validity dates, and terms, used when reviewing or editing procurement pricing agreements.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |
  | `id` | string (UUID) | Price list ID |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  - **Permission key**: `vendor_management.price_list:view`
  - **Roles**: Requestor, HOD, Purchase, Approval

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
      "no": "PL-2026-0001",
      "name": "Q2 2026 Beverage Price List",
      "status": "active",
      "vendor": {
        "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
        "name": "Bangkok Beverage Co., Ltd."
      },
      "currency": {
        "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
        "code": "THB"
      },
      "effective_from_date": "2026-04-01",
      "effective_to_date": "2026-06-30",
      "is_active": true,
      "pricelist_detail": [
        {
          "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
          "product_id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
          "product_name": "Sparkling Water 500ml",
          "unit_name": "Bottle",
          "price": 15.00,
          "moq_qty": 24,
          "is_active": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Bearer token missing or invalid |
  | 403 | User lacks `vendor_management.price_list:view` permission |
  | 404 | Price list not found |

  > Service-layer errors propagate via TCP; see micro-business for full list.
}

params:path {
  id: {{price_list_id}}
}
